  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_132",
    "english": "Demon. Although an inhabitant of the Demon Realm, they can be found in the human world, in places where demonic organizations lie, such as Tokyo Kingdom or Yomihara. Using their superhuman strength, they do work that requires physical power, especially one that requires violence, and some of them use weapons like claws with experience, building reputation in the underworld.",
